2153, "La ligne suivante indique la distance de votre cible et sa vitesse."

2154, "Notez les crochets autour de mon vaisseau indiquant que je suis votre cible actuelle."

2155, "Lorsque je vole hors de vue, l'indicateur hors écran s'affiche. Il indique la direction dans laquelle vous devez vous tourner pour faire face à votre cible."

2156, "L'indicateur se déplace en fonction de mes déplacements. Il est toujours pointé vers votre cible."

2157, "Remarquez comment les triangles se séparent. Plus ils sont éloignés, plus vous devrez vous tourner pour faire face à votre cible."

2158, "(fr)Finally, note the number by the indicator.  This is the distance to your target."

2159, "(fr)The circular gauge near the bottom of your HUD is the radar.  Friendly ships are shown in green.  Hostile ships appear in red. Ships directly in front of you appear in the radar's center."

2160, "(fr)Using your main flight controller turn your ship toward mine.  Stop when my ship is in your center reticle."

2161, "(fr)Good.  Now stay in that position."

2162, "Maintenant, tournez-vous à nouveau vers mon vaisseau."

2163, "(fr)[Press $m$] Match my speed."

2164, "Faites correspondre votre vitesse à la mienne à présent. Vous devez suivre les instructions si vous souhaitez compléter ce module."

2165, "(fr)To the left of the reticle is the speed gauge.  The capital M next to the current speed indicates that you are matching speed with your target."

2166, "(fr)Now I want you to accelerate [$a$] and move to within 125 meters of me.  Do not collide with my ship."

2167, "(fr)Good.  Now decelerate [$z$] to drop 200 meters behind me."

2168, "(fr)Well done.  Now let's practice using the afterburner.  [$tab$]  Engage your afterburner, pilot."

2169, "(fr)The gauge to the left of your speed gauge displays remaining afterburner power.  Note that your engines consume it rapidly."

2170, "(fr)That extra speed is useful for quick, evasive maneuvers and closing large distances.  Maintain your maximum top speed. [$\$]  Try it now."

2171, "(fr)Now bring your fighter to a complete stop. [$backspace$]"

2172, "(fr)Drone 01 has jumped in.  Target it. [Press $t$]"

2173, "(fr)Good.  Now follow me.  Note how your speed automatically changes to match mine."

2174, "(fr)The gauge to the left of your speed gauge indicates remaining afterburner power.  Note that it is consumed rapidly."

2175, "(fr)Good.  Now fly within 100 units of it and come to a stop.  [$backspace$]  Be careful not to fly too fast."

2176, "(fr)Well done.  Note that it takes some time to come to a complete stop."

2177, "(fr)Now fire your primary weapon [press $left ctrl$] at Drone 01.  Hit it a few times, but do not destroy it."

2178, "(fr)You had orders not to destroy Drone 01, pilot."

2179, "(fr)Near the center of your HUD, the hull integrity of your target is displayed.  Notice that it has dropped from 100%."

2180, "Ces informations sont également disponibles dans le coin supérieur droit de votre vue cible."

2181, "(fr)Now destroy Drone 01. [Press $left ctrl$]"

2182, "Bon travail."

2183, "(fr)Let's see how quickly you can destroy these new drones.  Target hostiles [$h$] and destroy them with your Subach HL-7. [Press $left ctrl$] The HL-7 is standard issue on all Myrmidon space superiority fighters."

2184, "(fr)Well done. This concludes module TSM-103c."

2185, "La plupart des sorties se terminent par un ordre de retour à la base. Ne quittez pas la zone d'engagement avant d'y avoir été autorisé."

2186, "(fr)Your navigation computer will be programmed with the proper coordinates. All you need to do is engage your subspace drive. Do this now. [$Alt-J$]"

