2209, "(fr)In combat, you will need to acquire your targets quickly. With multiple wings and warships, you will not have time to cycle through all objects in sensor range to find a specific target. Let's take a look at some controls that will help you locate targets more efficiently."

2210, "Deux drones seront utilisés pour la première partie de cet exercice."

2211, "(fr)You have a targeting control which enables you to acquire the nearest hostile target [$h$]. Using the control repeatedly will cycle through hostile targets in order of their proximity."

